Package: nikto
Version: 2.6.0
Architecture: all
Maintainer: Alienkrishn [Anon4You]
Depends: perl, git, openssl, openssl-tool, clang, make, cmake, curl, pkg-config
Section: security
Priority: optional
Homepage: https://github.com/sullo/nikto
Description: Comprehensive web server scanner
 Nikto performs comprehensive tests against web servers
 for dangerous files, outdated servers, and vulnerabilities.
 Supports SSL, proxies, and multiple IDS evasion techniques.
